"Adrenaline Control"    
        The psionicist alters the flow of adrenaline in his own body to
        provide himself with short boosts of speed or strength.  The 
        psionicist gets a temporary increase in either strength or 
  	dexterity based on guild level.
 
SP Cost:  Variable	Guild Level:  5		Potential Points:  2
 
Command:  adrenalize <str/dex>
